else. As I cannot complete the tomb of Julius I should prefer, if I am called upon to give satisfaction for what I have received, to let that satisfaction be in money instead of in work, as I should not have time for the latter course. I do not know what else to say, because I am not in touch with the matter and do not know what stage you have reached with it. As to the suggestion of making the tomb of Julius against the wall, like that of Pius, I am in favour of it, and there could be no more expeditious way found of carrying it out. I have nothing more to add except this, that you must now leave my affairs and your own to look after themselves and come back here, for I understand that the plague is raging with great virulence: and I would rather have you alive than get my business settled. Come back, therefore. If I die before the Pope there will be no occasion to settle anything; if I live I am certain the Pope will settle the matter for me, either now or later on. Come back, therefore. Yesterday I was with your mother and I advised her, in the presence of Granaccio and of the turner Giovanni, to make you come back.\r","standoffProperties":[{"id":"701e205c-aba7-40e4-bad8-213ab739864d","type":"style/uppercase","start":0,"end":21,"value":"","text":"Messer Giovanfrancesc","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"ee781355-ce06-433d-b7de-8191ef23e3d6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":0,"end":21,"value":"a4393234-2745-42ec-ba3e-42e4c52edb0c","text":"Messer Giovanfrancesc","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"df75e2be-1001-4c48-a64a-dcaa205081c0","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":26,"end":26,"value":"add92e01-cefe-4f13-94dd-f00eb82155b0","text":"","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"a1bbc802-9e99-404f-afbb-5e4ee91e74a6","type":"codex/entity-reference","start":49,"end":50,"value":"19c867c5-e13e-42c9-91b8-123a70b28dce","text":"t","metadata":{},"plugin":null,"isDeleted":false},{"id":"4ad8249a-7743-4140-91dc-f6a7b